how many bands have played here

3
00:00:40,915 --> 00:00:42,625
and then ended up being huge.

4
00:00:43,710 --> 00:00:45,128
We're gonna be legends.

5
00:00:47,047 --> 00:00:49,382
Eat up, boys, 'cause after tonight,

6
00:00:50,258 --> 00:00:51,718
everything changes.

7
00:01:02,854 --> 00:01:03,980
Is this seat taken?

8
00:01:14,115 --> 00:01:15,575
