9
00:01:19,788 --> 00:01:20,914
Yeah, I messed up.

10
00:01:22,290 --> 00:01:23,541
No, it's like you said...

11
00:01:24,542 --> 00:01:26,127
you know, you didn't have a choice.

12
00:01:26,878 --> 00:01:28,505
I mean, Caleb owns your soul.

13
00:01:28,588 --> 00:01:30,048
No.

14
00:01:30,131 --> 00:01:33,802
No, still, I know what he's capable of.
I brought you guys right to him.

15
00:01:33,885 --> 00:01:36,387
