-Um,

39
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:50,962
sorry I couldn't stay for the whole thing.

40
00:02:51,045 --> 00:02:53,506
-I had a ton of homework.
-It's fine. Thanks for coming.

41
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:54,757
Thanks for inviting me.

42
00:02:56,217 --> 00:02:57,051
See you around.

43
00:02:57,135 --> 00:02:58,428
So, um, listen.

44
00:02:58,511 --> 00:03:01,347
Since we make such a great team,
you know, with dance and everything...

45
00:03:01,431 --> 00:03:05,351
and, uh, you have an A in history,
any chance we could be study partners?

46
00:03:05,977 --> 00:03:07,770
I'd love to,

47
00:03:07,854 --> 00:03:10,481
but with the band,
I'm not sure I'll have any free time.

48
00:03:10,565 --> 00:03:11,441
Sorry.

49
00:03:11,524 --> 00:03:13,276
Oh, nah, no worries. Um...

50
00:03:13,902 --> 00:03:15,111
Then, I'll ask you this:

51
00:03:16,487 --> 00:03:18,823
