150
00:07:31,534 --> 00:07:32,410
OK, look.

151
00:07:32,952 --> 00:07:36,789
I... I just wanted to know more about you,
you know, just curious. Um...

152
00:07:37,331 --> 00:07:40,084
So, I came here last week
on your birthday.

153
00:07:40,626 --> 00:07:41,752
