154
00:07:42,253 --> 00:07:44,088
Even after all your speeches
about boundaries?

155
00:07:44,172 --> 00:07:45,798
-You were spying on me?
-I know.

156
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:47,717
I'm sorry. It was wrong.

157
00:07:48,801 --> 00:07:50,136
But I'm worried about you.

158
00:07:50,887 --> 00:07:52,096
